%%{init: {'theme':'base','themeVariables':{'fontSize':'14px'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant FE as AvatarCard + useProfileAvatar (browser)
    participant API as NestJS API (JWT guard)
    participant S3 as Object storage (private)
    participant DB as MongoDB (users)
    participant CDN as CloudFront CDN

    rect rgb(237,233,254)
    Note over U,CDN: UPLOAD a new photo
    U->>FE: choose file
    FE->>FE: validate type (jpeg/png/webp) + size (<=5MB)
    FE->>API: POST /api/me/avatar/upload-url {contentType}
    API->>API: request-avatar-upload.prepare<br/>buildAvatarKey = avatars/{userId} + presign POST (size cap)
    API-->>FE: AvatarUploadTicket {url, fields, key, expiresInSeconds}
    FE->>S3: POST file (form fields + file) to presigned URL
    S3-->>FE: 204 No Content
    FE->>API: PUT /api/me/avatar {key}
    API->>API: set-avatar.confirm<br/>owns key? headObject exists? size+type ok?
    API->>API: resolve srcUrl (CDN url + ?v= cache-bust)
    API->>DB: updateAvatar { srcUrl, key }
    API-->>FE: AvatarResult { avatarUrl }
    FE->>FE: updateCurrentUser({...currentUser, avatarUrl}) -> Redux
    end

    rect rgb(219,234,254)
    Note over U,CDN: READ everywhere (topbar, sidebar, messages)
    U->>CDN: GET avatarUrl (https cdn/avatars/{userId}?v=...)
    CDN->>S3: origin fetch via OAC (cache miss only)
    CDN-->>U: image bytes, cached at edge
    end

    rect rgb(254,226,226)
    Note over U,CDN: REMOVE the photo
    U->>API: DELETE /api/me/avatar
    API->>API: remove-avatar.remove
    API->>DB: getUserRecord (read previous key)
    API->>DB: clearAvatar (avatar = null)
    API->>S3: deleteObjectBestEffort(previousKey)
    API-->>FE: AvatarResult { avatarUrl: null }
    FE->>FE: updateCurrentUser -> initials fallback
    end
